echo bay ha nevada gold discoveri echo bay mine ltd said it discov a gold deposit in the cove area near it mccoy gold mine in nevada . echo bay said it encount gold in 39 of 42 drill hole at cove . it said seven hole averag 0.185 ounc gold a short ton and 1.8 ounc of silver , with the seven intersect averag 118 feet in thick beneath 25 feet of overburden . the discoveri is on the mccoy properti , one mile northeast of the mccoy open pit , heap leach gold mine , which is expect to produc about 85,000 ounc of gold thi year , echo bay said .